《娜样说》曲长3分29秒<ref name="itunes">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/talk-that-talk-deluxe-edition/id479321646|title=Rihanna – Talk That Talk (Deluxe Edition)|publisher=[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]] (US). [[Apple_Inc|Apple Inc]]|accessdate=2012-03-26|archive-date=2016-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160208191209/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/talk-that-talk-deluxe-edition/id479321646|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》杂志的克萊爾·南達特（Claire Suddath）归纳其为一首精力充沛的[[嘻哈音乐|嘻哈]]并使用了[[流行音乐|流行音乐]]来挂钩的歌曲<ref name="Time">{{cite web|url=http://entertainment.time.com/2011/11/21/music-monday-rihannas-talk-that-talk/|title=Album Review: Rihanna's Talk That Talk|work=[[时代_(杂志)|Time]]|last=Suddath|first=Claire|date=2011-11-21|accessdate=2011-11-25|archive-date=2015-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151128071424/http://entertainment.time.com/2011/11/21/music-monday-rihannas-talk-that-talk/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其同时使用了[[节奏蓝调|节奏蓝调]]的[[节拍|节拍]]<ref name="digital spy">{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/singlesreviews/a370952/rihanna-ft-jay-z-talk-that-talk-single-review.html|title=Rihanna ft. Jay-Z: 'Talk That Talk' – Single review|work=Digital Spy|last=Corner|first=Lewis|date=2012-03-13|accessdate=2013-08-20|archive-date=2013-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130703175124/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/singlesreviews/a370952/rihanna-ft-jay-z-talk-that-talk-single-review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、「强烈鼓声」、粗俗的[[合成器|合成器]]作为伴奏<ref name="RapUp1"/>，并以嘻哈歌手[[声名狼藉先生|声名狼藉先生]]的歌曲《我有个故事要诉说》（''I Got a Story to Tell''）作为采样<ref name="Spy"/>。

《[[每日邮报|每日邮报]]》的阿德里安·特里尔斯（Adrian Thrills）称这首歌是「慢而迷人的」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/reviews/article-2063019/Rihanna-Talk-That-Talk-music-review-RnB-queen-says-loud.html|title=It seems even pop's most provocative princess is a romantic at heart... Rihanna reveals she just wants love|work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|last=Thrills|first=Adrian|date=2011-11-18|accessdate=2011-11-18|archive-date=2017-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170108033909/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/reviews/article-2063019/Rihanna-Talk-That-Talk-music-review-RnB-queen-says-loud.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[MTV|MTV吸睛]]的萨姆·蘭斯基（Sam Lansky）同样认为其的性感和自信，并观察到当蕾哈娜演唱歌曲的[[副歌|副歌]]时所产生的价值<ref name="buzzworthy">{{cite web|url=http://buzzworthy.mtv.com/2011/11/21/rihanna-talk-that-talk/|title=Rihanna's 'Talk That Talk': A Track-By-Track Guide To Her New Album|publisher=MTV Buzzworthy|last=Lansky|first=Sam|date=2011-11-21|accessdate=2013-08-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6AgHKV9sU?url=http://buzzworthy.mtv.com/2011/11/21/rihanna-talk-that-talk/|archivedate=2012-09-14}}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]的乍得·格里紹（Chad Grischow）写道那个「模糊不清合成器的旋律」似乎在插嘴着蕾哈娜那「为了可以枕边情话而性感恳求着」，更为「杰斯那爱珠宝的饶舌」所增色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/11/22/rihanna-talk-that-talk-review|title=Rihanna: Talk That Talk Review|publisher=IGN|last=Grischow|first=Chad|date=2011-11-22|accessdate=2013-08-20|archive-date=2016-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419213134/http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/11/22/rihanna-talk-that-talk-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[數碼間諜|數碼間諜]]的罗伯特·科普塞（Robert Copsey）感觉該歌的[[固定低音|反复乐节]]与蕾哈娜2010年的单曲《[[坏孩子_(歌曲)|坏孩子]]》有相似之处<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/albumreviews/a351462/rihanna-talk-that-talk-album-review.html|title=Rihanna: 'Talk That Talk' – Album review|work=Digital Spy|last=Copsey|first=Robert|date=2011-11-21|accessdate=2013-08-22|archive-date=2013-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605043843/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/albumreviews/a351462/rihanna-talk-that-talk-album-review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

这首歌一开始是杰斯的饶舌部分，那些歌词包括：「I talk big money，I talk big homes/I sell out arenas，I call that getting dome/Million dollar voice，came through phone/We heading to the top，if you coming，come on」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rapfix.mtv.com/2011/11/13/rihanna-talk-that-talk-new-song-with-jay-z/|title=Rihanna Drops 'Talk That Talk' Single Featuring Jay-Z|publisher=MTV News|last=D.L.|first=Chandler|date=2011-11-13|accessdate=2011-11-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111114170342/http://rapfix.mtv.com/2011/11/13/rihanna-talk-that-talk-new-song-with-jay-z/|archivedate=2011-11-14}}</ref>。他那慢速度的饶舌还有歌词中的双关语，而获得了一些幽默的评论，其中包括克萊爾·南達特一个谈及性的观点，暗示了杰斯对于这首歌的享受程度：「跟她的膀胱发生性关系，她就像『哦，我要去尿尿！』。」<ref name="Time"/>

